# TownSquare Web - Development Rules

## Icons
- **NEVER use custom SVG elements** - Always use Phosphor React icons from `phosphor-react` package
- Import icons: `import { IconName } from 'phosphor-react';`
- Use with props: `<IconName size={16} weight="bold" />`

## Styling
- Use Tailwind CSS utility classes
- Follow 8pt grid spacing system
- Brand colors defined in `tailwind.config.ts`

## Components
- Mark components using Phosphor icons as `'use client';`
- Keep components in `/components/landing/` directory
